s here. For other uses, see <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./List_of_things_named_after_Leonhard_Euler#Euler's_numbers" title="List of things named after Leonhard Euler">List of things named after Leonhard Euler §<span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span>Euler's numbers</a>.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" about="#mwt2" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Redirect","href":"./Template:Redirect"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"E (number)"},"2":{"wt":"the codes representing food additives"},"3":{"wt":"E number"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAw">"E (number)" redirects here. For the codes representing food additives, see <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./E_number" title="E number">E number</a>.</div>
<link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Wikipedia_indefinitely_move-protected_pages#E%20(mathematical%20constant)" about="#mwt3" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"pp-move-indef","href":"./Template:Pp-move-indef"},"params":{"small":{"wt":"yes"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBA"/>
<figure class="mw-halign-right" typeof="mw:Image/Thumb" id="mwBQ"><a href="./File:Hyperbola_E.svg" id="mwBg"><img resource="./File:Hyperbola_E.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Hyperbola_E.svg/237px-Hyperbola_E.svg.png" data-file-width="609" data-file-height="652" data-file-type="drawing" height="254" width="237" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Hyperbola_E.svg/474px-Hyperbola_E.svg.png 2x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e8/Hyperbola_E.svg/356px-Hyperbola_E.svg.png 1.5x" id="mwBw"/></a><figcaption id="mwCA">Graph of the equation <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt259" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"y=1/x."}}' id="mwCQ"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle y=1/x.}">
