<p id="mwrw">In particular, the probability of winning zero times (<span class="texhtml " about="#mwt107" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"math","href":"./Template:Math"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"&apos;&apos;k&apos;&apos; = 0"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwsA"><i>k</i> = 0</span>) is</p>
<dl id="mwsQ"><dd id="mwsg"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt433" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\\left(1-\\frac{1}{10^6}\\right)^{10^6}."}}' id="mwsw"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \left(1-{\frac {1}{10^{6}}}\right)^{10^{6}}.}">
