<p id="mwtA">This is very close to the limit</p>
<dl id="mwtQ"><dd id="mwtg"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt435" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\\lim_{n\\to\\infty} \\left(1-\\frac{1}{n}\\right)^n = \\frac{1}{e}."}}' id="mwtw"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \lim _{n\to \infty }\left(1-{\frac {1}{n}}\right)^{n}={\frac {1}{e}}.}">
