  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/0b537c6a60fa46f3a9f01d48e1b279e036b28037" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.338ex; width:7.706ex; height:2.676ex;" alt="{\displaystyle x^{-1}\ln x}"/></span><span about="#mwt443">
</span> occurs at <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt447" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"x=e"}}' id="mw1g"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle x=e}">
