</span> (<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Steiner's_calculus_problem" title="Steiner's calculus problem" id="mw1w">Steiner's problem</a>, discussed <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./E_(mathematical_constant)#Exponential-like_functions" id="mw2A">below</a>).  The quantity <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt445" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"x^{-1}\\ln x"}}' id="mw2Q"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle x^{-1}\ln x}">
