</span> is a measure of <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Shannon_information" title="Shannon information" id="mw2g" class="mw-redirect">information</a> gleaned from an event occurring with probability <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt449" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"1/x "}}' id="mw2w"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle 1/x}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
