</span></dd></dl>

<p id="mwAR8">The parenthesized limit on the right is independent of the <span class="nowrap" about="#mwt163" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"nowrap","href":"./Template:Nowrap"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"variable {{math|&apos;&apos;x&apos;&apos;}}:"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwASA">variable <span class="texhtml "><i>x</i></span>:</span> it depends only on the <span class="nowrap" about="#mwt164" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"nowrap","href":"./Template:Nowrap"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"base {{math|&apos;&apos;a&apos;&apos;}}."}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwASE">base <span class="texhtml "><i>a</i></span>.</span> When the base is set <span class="nowrap" about="#mwt165" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"nowrap","href":"./Template:Nowrap"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"to {{mvar|e}},"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwASI">to <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;">e</span>,</span> this limit is equal <span class="nowrap" about="#mwt166" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"nowrap","href":"./Template:Nowrap"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"to {{math|1}},"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwASM">to <span class="texhtml ">1</span>,</span> and so <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;" about="#mwt167" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"mvar","href":"./Template:Mvar"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"e"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwASQ">e</span> is symbolically defined by the equation:</p>
<dl id="mwASU"><dd id="mwASY"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt466" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\\frac{d}{dx}e^x = e^x."}}' id="mwASc"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {\frac {d}{dx}}e^{x}=e^{x}.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
