</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/dbefeb5e424ed3a0840aaedf1b792b2f94b9ee24" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.338ex; width:13.199ex; height:5.843ex;" alt="\int _{1}^{e}{\frac {1}{t}}\,dt=1."/></span><span about="#mwt484">
</span></dd></dl>
</li>
<li id="mwAXw"> If <span class="texhtml " about="#mwt212" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"math","href":"./Template:Math"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"&apos;&apos;f&apos;&apos;(&apos;&apos;t&apos;&apos;)"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAX0"><i>f</i>(<i>t</i>)</span> is an <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Exponential_function" title="Exponential function" id="mwAX4">exponential function</a>, then the quantity <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt486" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":" \\tau = f(t)/f&apos;(t)"}}' id="mwAX8"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \tau =f(t)/f'(t)}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mi>τ<!-- τ --></mi>
        <mo>=</mo>
        <mi>f</mi>
        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
        <mi>t</mi>
        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>
        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mo>/</mo>
        </mrow>
