</section></section><section data-mw-section-id="11" id="mwAYU"><h2 id="Properties">Properties</h2>

<section data-mw-section-id="12" id="mwAYY"><h3 id="Calculus">Calculus</h3>
<p id="mwAYc">As in the motivation, the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Exponential_function" title="Exponential function" id="mwAYg">exponential function</a> <span class="texhtml " about="#mwt214" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"math","href":"./Template:Math"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"&apos;&apos;e&apos;&apos;&lt;sup>&apos;&apos;x&apos;&apos;&lt;/sup>"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAYk"><i>e</i><sup><i>x</i></sup></span> is important in part because it is the unique nontrivial function (up to multiplication by a constant) which is its own <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Derivative" title="Derivative" id="mwAYo">derivative</a></p>

<dl id="mwAYs"><dd id="mwAYw"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt490" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\\frac{d}{dx}e^x = e^x"}}' id="mwAY0"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {\frac {d}{dx}}e^{x}=e^{x}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
          <mfrac>
            <mi>d</mi>
            <mrow>
              <mi>d</mi>
              <mi>x</mi>
            </mrow>
          </mfrac>
        </mrow>
        <msup>
          <mi>e</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>x</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mo>=</mo>
        <msup>
          <mi>e</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>x</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle {\frac {d}{dx}}e^{x}=e^{x}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/c432d20d9a75e0f41d682184fa4b640357c3d6b3" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.005ex; width:10.992ex; height:5.509ex;" alt="{\frac  {d}{dx}}e^{x}=e^{x}"/></span><span about="#mwt490">
</span></dd></dl>

<p id="mwAY4">and therefore its own <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Antiderivative" title="Antiderivative" id="mwAY8">antiderivative</a> as well:</p>

<dl id="mwAZA"><dd id="mwAZE"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt492" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\\int e^x\\,dx = e^x + C ."}}' id="mwAZI"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle \int e^{x}\,dx=e^{x}+C.}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mo>∫<!-- ∫ --></mo>
        <msup>
          <mi>e</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>x</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mspace width="thinmathspace"></mspace>
        <mi>d</mi>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo>=</mo>
        <msup>
          <mi>e</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>x</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
        <mo>+</mo>
        <mi>C</mi>
        <mo>.</mo>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle \int e^{x}\,dx=e^{x}+C.}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/c59b6f0fdaa20f0b4adccc7a18d91bdf6ae4f602" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -2.338ex; width:18.377ex; height:5.676ex;" alt="{\displaystyle \int e^{x}\,dx=e^{x}+C.}"/></span><span about="#mwt492">
</span></dd></dl>

