</span></dd></dl>

</section><section data-mw-section-id="17" id="mwAik"><h3 id="Differential_equations">Differential equations</h3>
<p id="mwAio">The general function</p>

<dl id="mwAis"><dd id="mwAiw"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt573" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"y(x) = Ce^x"}}' id="mwAi0"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle y(x)=Ce^{x}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
      <mstyle displaystyle="true" scriptlevel="0">
        <mi>y</mi>
        <mo stretchy="false">(</mo>
        <mi>x</mi>
        <mo stretchy="false">)</mo>
        <mo>=</mo>
        <mi>C</mi>
        <msup>
          <mi>e</mi>
          <mrow class="MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
            <mi>x</mi>
          </mrow>
        </msup>
      </mstyle>
    </mrow>
    <annotation encoding="application/x-tex">{\displaystyle y(x)=Ce^{x}}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src="https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/3f3739d1e217e05ef9d60460bd8dd478c507b4a6" class="mwe-math-fallback-image-inline" aria-hidden="true" style="vertical-align: -0.838ex; width:11.415ex; height:2.843ex;" alt="{\displaystyle y(x)=Ce^{x}}"/></span><span about="#mwt573">
</span></dd></dl>

<p id="mwAi4">is the solution to the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Differential_equation" title="Differential equation" id="mwAi8">differential equation</a>:</p>

<dl id="mwAjA"><dd id="mwAjE"><span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt575" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"y&apos; = y ."}}' id="mwAjI"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle y'=y.}">
