<p id="mwAlI">This continued fraction for <span class="texhtml mvar" style="font-style:italic;" about="#mwt311" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"mvar","href":"./Template:Mvar"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"e"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAlM">e</span> converges three times as quickly:<link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:All_articles_with_unsourced_statements" about="#mwt312" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cn","href":"./Template:Cn"},"params":{"date":{"wt":"September 2018"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAlQ"/><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Articles_with_unsourced_statements_from_September_2018" about="#mwt312"/><sup class="noprint Inline-Template Template-Fact" style="white-space:nowrap;" about="#mwt312" id="mwAlU"><span typeof="mw:Entity">[</span><i><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Wikipedia:Citation_needed" title="Wikipedia:Citation needed"><span title="This claim needs references to reliable sources. (September 2018)">citation needed</span></a></i><span typeof="mw:Entity">]</span></sup></p>
