</span> ubi </i>e<i id="mwA00"> denotat numerum, cuius logarithmus hyperbolicus est 1.</i>  (So it [i.e., <i id="mwA04">c</i>, the speed] will be <span class="mwe-math-element" typeof="mw:Extension/math" about="#mwt425" data-mw='{"name":"math","attrs":{},"body":{"extsrc":"\\frac{dc}{c} = \\frac{dy ds}{rdx}"}}' id="mwA08"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;" id="mwA1A"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\displaystyle {\frac {dc}{c}}={\frac {dyds}{rdx}}}" id="mwA1E">
